	(text "IO SHEET — populate following docs/03-schematic-spec.md SHEET 3\n\nBlocks:\n  3.1  Buffer PWM 3V3->5V : U4 (SN74AHCT244PWR) + C_buf\n  3.2  Pots 5 voies        : J9-J13 + filtre RC R_pot/C_pot par voie\n  3.3  Bouton E-STOP       : SW1 + R_estop + C_estop + D_estop\n  3.4  Switch mode SPDT    : SW4 + R_mode\n  3.5  Buzzer alarme       : BZ1 + Q3 + R_bz + D_bz\n\nADC inputs use ADC1 only (GPIO 1, 2, 4, 5, 6) — compatible WiFi.\nU4 OE pins tied to GND (always enabled).\nUnused U4 inputs (2A2-2A4) tied to GND or left floating with OE high."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
